Appetize Point of Sale technology brings value to hundreds of enterprise businesses in sports &
entertainment, education, convention centers, dining, theme parks and more.





Quick Service
Appetize Fast Casual Restaurant solution is designed to be the fastest, easiest to use front-of-house POS for cashiers with powerful management tools for back-of-house users.

Learn More





Retail
Appetize Retail Mode includes dependable support for bar code scanning, unlimited SKUs, and easy inventory management tools for smarter merchandising.

Learn More





Table Service
Appetize Restaurant Mode includes support for all varieties of site restaurant use, including reservations, table layouts, and coursing.

Learn More














Proven at Scale
Our customers are the largest foodservice providers, management companies, and chains. That’s why we focus all development on fast transactions – on or offline – with the most reliable, most secure payment solutions available.





Get Demo

















Future-forward Technology
Cloud-based, redundant architecture built on the best of today’s tablet and mobile technology. Appetize is the only truly modern, enterprise Point of Sale.





Get Demo

















Powerful ROI Reporting and Inventory Management
Robust real-time reporting, cash room management, ingredient-level inventory details and more. Appetize back of house tools are designed to give you insights that drive revenue, not just data.





