Company Overview of Appetize Technologies Inc.



Snapshot People




Company Overview
Appetize Technologies Inc. develops enterprise point of sale and inventory management solutions. The company’s solutions provides auto offline mode services; back of house control services, such as inventory management, analytics, menu management, social engagement, and fan data; various payment methods; mobile ordering; and support services. It offers its solutions for sports and entertainment, education, and leisure businesses. The company was founded in 2011 and is based in Santa Monica, California.


1601 Colorado AvenueSanta Monica, CA 90404United StatesFounded in 2011



Phone: 415-947-2470

www.appetizeapp.com







