Appetize is a modern Point of Sale, inventory and analytics company transforming how restaurants, quick serve chains and business dining corporations manage and process guest transactions. Its revenue-generating platform includes fixed terminals, handheld devices for table side ordering and self-serve kiosks that seamlessly sync with a dynamic and easy to use Kitchen Display System. Advanced reporting, inventory management and ingredient-level reporting give powerful insights into how efficiently your restaurant is running. 
For more information, please visit www.appetizeapp.com.


