Christopher Harrison - San Francisco, California, Appetize Technologies, Inc. | about.meChristopher HarrisonSenior Sales Executive in San Francisco, CaliforniaVisit my company websiteI have more than 20 years of hospitality industry experience and have worked with hundreds of top tier organizations throughout North America. My expertise with hospitality software solutions comes from a combination of experience in sales, programming and operations management; my innate passion for the world of hospitality comes from a lifelong pursuit of exceptional service and the great fortune I have had to work with some of the restaurant world's most successful and influential restaurateurs and chefs.In my current role I am responsible for helping stadiums and entertainment venues invest in next-generation Point of Sale and payments solutions for Appetize Technologies. Appetize is a sports & entertainment focused, cloud-based Point of Sale platform based in Los Angeles, CA. The company's core focus is to provide entertainment venues with a state of the art dynamic ordering suite of POS solutions.Appetize offers a fully capable point-of-sale solution that provides a dynamic front of house ordering tool set with a full back of house suite of management modules that include inventory, suites & catering, time keeping, operational reports and data analytic tools. We provide a tablet based point-of-sale system that transacts cash, credit and a variety of digital payments methods like Apple Pay, Google Wallet and Beacon technology. Our solutions include a variety of form factors that will provide your team with the ability to cater to a wide range of service areas within your facility that include the typical concessions stand, club and restaurants , luxury suites, line busting, kiosk self-ordering, hawkers, and parking lot attendants, as well as fan facing mobile ordering for pickup and/or delivery.#cycling#mountainbiking#skiing#golf#photographyWorkAppetize Technologies, Inc.